   Baek, You Soon; Covey, Paul A.; Bedinger, Patricia A., Colorado State Univ, Dept Biol, Ft Collins, CO 80523 USA.
   Petersen, Jennifer J.; Chetelat, Roger T., Univ Calif Davis, Dept Plant Sci, Davis, CA 95616 USA.
   McClure, Bruce, Univ Missouri, Dept Biochem, Columbia, MO 65211 USA.},
