   Univ Arizona, Ctr Insect Sci, Tucson, AZ 85721 USA.
   Univ Arizona, ARL Div Neurobiol, Tucson, AZ 85721 USA.
   Univ Arizona, Dept Ecol \& Evolutionary Biol, Tucson, AZ 85721 USA.
   Arizona Sonora Desert Museum, Tucson, AZ USA.},
